\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_8420145\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 01, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104guc1665702710864_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/guc1665702710864_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/guc1665702710864_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"guc1665702710864\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Fixed Length of Entity\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Physical size of the entity or included entity, in characters.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"guc1665702710864__section_ihw_zwg_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1111154e51\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"guc1665702710864__p_d7337e1_d7338e1_d7339e1\">There is no restriction on the length of an entity or the\n            number of occurrences it can contain, so there is no default for this field.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"guc1665702710864__p_d7340e1_d7341e1_d7342e1\">You should define a fixed length for an entity if:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"guc1665702710864__ul_dqc_cxg_pwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"guc1665702710864__li_d3599e1_d3600e1_d3601e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"guc1665702710864__p_d7343e1_d7344e1_d7345e1\">The entity is an included entity. Specify the\n                  number of bytes available in the remainder of the occurrence in the parent\n                  entity.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"guc1665702710864__li_d3602e1_d3603e1_d3604e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"guc1665702710864__p_d7346e1_d7347e1_d7348e1\">You want to override the way Uniface generates the\n                  length of the overflow table in a record-level DBMS.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"guc1665702710864__section_vmb_dxg_pwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1111154e78\">Applies to</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"guc1665702710864__ul_ptq_dxg_pwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"guc1665702710864__li_d39734e1_d39735e1_d39736e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hzd1665702710226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hzd1665702710226.html\" title=\"A Modeled Entity Interface is a Development Object that defines a reusable value for the Database Interface property of a Database Entity.\">Modeled Entity Interface</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420145\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8420145\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Fixed Length of Entity Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 01, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Fixed Length of Entity Physical size of the entity or included entity, in characters. Description There is no restriction on the length of an entity or the number of occurrences it can contain, so there is no default for this field. You should define a fixed length for an entity if: The entity is an included entity. Specify the number of bytes available in the remainder of the occurrence in the parent entity. You want to override the way Uniface generates the length of the overflow table in a record-level DBMS. Applies to Modeled Entity Interface Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}